<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>世界計畫 繽紛舞台 - 角色介紹</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #33ccff;
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .profile-img {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 200px;
        }
        .char-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .char-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-top: 5px solid #33ccff;
        }
        h2 { color: #0088cc; }
        footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #888; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>世界計畫 繽紛舞台！</h1>
    <p>介紹那些在音樂世界中閃耀的角色們</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <img src="https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/xzwhOQifajLeLvr4UQnU-D7FAS8ENUxnOwUoDzoT247td9a6qfYRLKuy3JIfwIcfKI1nB7cGGkVN6FWu9wDDeQ=w526-h296-rw" alt="世界計畫角色圖" class="profile-img">

    <section>
        <h2>核心虛擬歌手</h2>
        <div class="char-grid">
            <div class="char-card">
                <h3>初音未來 (Hatsune Miku)</h3>
                <p>存在於「世界」的虛擬歌手，引導著內心擁有煩惱的少年少女們。</p>
            </div>
            </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>主要團體</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Leoneed</strong>：由兒時玩伴組成的樂團。</li>
            <li><strong>MORE MORE JUMP!</strong>：帶出希望的偶像團體。</li>
            <li><strong>Vivid BAD SQUAD</strong>：追求超越傳說的街頭團體。</li>
            <li><strong>Wonderlands×Showtime</strong>：充滿活力的舞台劇團體。</li>
            <li><strong>25點，Nightcord見。</strong>：深夜活動的神祕音樂團體。</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Project Sekai Fan Page</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
